- icaRius Game Quest was made by modding a former quest, Zelda Return of the Hylian, 
initially developped by Vincent Jouillat, then adapted for Solarus Game Engine
by the Solarus team. More information on the root quest used here :
https://gitlab.com/solarus-games/zelda-roth-se/-/blob/dev/license.txt

- This quest was made using the Solarus Game Engine. 
More information on Solarus Game Engine here :
https://gitlab.com/solarus-games/solarus/-/blob/dev/license.txt

- More detailed information about the authors and license of every file
is displayed when you open this project with Solarus Quest Editor.
